398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_cricket_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_cricket_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the job\", \"from\": 946, \"to\": 953}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His family has been running Hillview Park Holsteins since 1956 and he has been showing cows himself since he was a young boy.\", \"from\": 989, \"to\": 1114, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His family\", \"from\": 989, \"to\": 999}, {\"ngram\": \"Hillview Park Holsteins\", \"from\": 1017, \"to\": 1040}, {\"ngram\": \"cows\", \"from\": 1076, \"to\": 1080}, {\"ngram\": \"a young boy\", \"from\": 1102, \"to\": 1113}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His family milk 300 cows and Callum said he is always looking to improve the next generation.\", \"from\": 1116, \"to\": 1209, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1145, \"end\": 1151, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Callum_Rebecchi\", \"score\": 0.9999836393182302, \"rank\": 1.225926034990382e-05, \"text\": \"Callum\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Callum_Rebecchi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Callum_Rebecchi\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His family\", \"from\": 1116, \"to\": 1126}, {\"ngram\": \"300 cows\", \"from\": 1132, \"to\": 1140}, {\"ngram\": \"the next generation\", \"from\": 1189, \"to\": 1208}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The goal is always to breed an animal good enough to compete in the show ring,\\\" Callum said.\", \"from\": 1211, \"to\": 1304, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1292, \"end\": 1298, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Callum_Rebecchi\", \"score\": 0.9999836393182302, \"rank\": 1.225926034990382e-05, \"text\": \"Callum\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Callum_Rebecchi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Callum_Rebecchi\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The goal\", \"from\": 1212, \"to\": 1220}, {\"ngram\": \"an animal\", \"from\": 1240, \"to\": 1249}, {\"ngram\": \"the show ring\", \"from\": 1276, \"to\": 1289}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He is looking forward to heading to Belgium and taking on the role of a mentor.\", \"from\": 1306, \"to\": 1385, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1342, \"end\": 1349, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\", \"score\": 0.9932946858443038, \"rank\": 0.006434677005252607, \"text\": \"Belgium\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the role\", \"from\": 1364, \"to\": 1372}, {\"ngram\": \"a mentor\", \"from\": 1376, \"to\": 1384}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I guess my role will be to use my experience to help the team if they run into a problem and to drive them around as well,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1387, \"to\": 1520, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my role\", \"from\": 1396, \"to\": 1403}, {\"ngram\": \"my experience\", \"from\": 1419, \"to\": 1432}, {\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 1441, \"to\": 1449}, {\"ngram\": \"a problem\", \"from\": 1467, \"to\": 1476}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It will be great to travel to Belgium and the networking and learning opportunities for the team will be amazing.\", \"from\": 1522, \"to\": 1636, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1553, \"end\": 1560, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\", \"score\": 0.9932946858443038, \"rank\": 0.006434677005252607, \"text\": \"Belgium\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the networking and learning opportunities\", \"from\": 1565, \"to\": 1606}, {\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 1611, \"to\": 1619}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It is still a competition, a bit like the cow Olympics, and we will be competitive and do Australia proud.\\\"\", \"from\": 1638, \"to\": 1746, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1729, \"end\": 1738, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9961713975426288, \"rank\": 0.0032289114268582116, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a competition\", \"from\": 1651, \"to\": 1664}, {\"ngram\": \"the cow Olympics\", \"from\": 1677, \"to\": 1693}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Organiser Justin Johnston said the trip was a great experience for young dairy farmers and it was something he wanted to see continue in the future.\", \"from\": 1748, \"to\": 1896, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1765, \"end\": 1773, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alan_Johnston\", \"score\": 0.9796744960506537, \"rank\": 0.01595019035978592, \"text\": \"Johnston\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alan_Johnston\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alan_Johnston\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the trip\", \"from\": 1779, \"to\": 1787}, {\"ngram\": \"a great experience\", \"from\": 1792, \"to\": 1810}, {\"ngram\": \"young dairy farmers\", \"from\": 1815, \"to\": 1834}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 1846, \"to\": 1855}, {\"ngram\": \"the future\", \"from\": 1885, \"to\": 1895}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Not only do the team get the opportunity to compete at the breeders school, they also get to take a look at some different farms in Holland including a barn, grazing and robot system.\", \"from\": 1898, \"to\": 2081, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2030, \"end\": 2037, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"score\": 0.9208613166889743, \"rank\": 0.07138174950445282, \"text\": \"Holland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 1910, \"to\": 1918}, {\"ngram\": \"the opportunity\", \"from\": 1923, \"to\": 1938}, {\"ngram\": \"the breeders school\", \"from\": 1953, \"to\": 1972}, {\"ngram\": \"a look\", \"from\": 1996, \"to\": 2002}, {\"ngram\": \"some different farms\", \"from\": 2006, \"to\": 2026}, {\"ngram\": \"a barn, grazing and robot system\", \"from\": 2048, \"to\": 2080}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They will also take a tour of a seed facility, among other things.\", \"from\": 2082, \"to\": 2148, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a tour\", \"from\": 2102, \"to\": 2108}, {\"ngram\": \"a seed facility\", \"from\": 2112, \"to\": 2127}, {\"ngram\": \"other things\", \"from\": 2135, \"to\": 2147}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was part of the first original trip back in 2019 and I thought the experience was invaluable so along with the committee (Simon Tognola, Julia Paulger and Brent Mitchell) we have made it happen, along with help from our sponsors,\\\" Justin said.\", \"from\": 2150, \"to\": 2396, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 2157, \"to\": 2161}, {\"ngram\": \"the first original trip\", \"from\": 2165, \"to\": 2188}, {\"ngram\": \"the experience\", \"from\": 2216, \"to\": 2230}, {\"ngram\": \"the committee\", \"from\": 2260, \"to\": 2273}, {\"ngram\": \"Simon Tognola\", \"from\": 2275, \"to\": 2288}, {\"ngram\": \"Julia Paulger\", \"from\": 2290, \"to\": 2303}, {\"ngram\": \"Brent Mitchell\", \"from\": 2308, \"to\": 2322}, {\"ngram\": \"help\", \"from\": 2359, \"to\": 2363}, {\"ngram\": \"our sponsors\", \"from\": 2369, \"to\": 2381}, {\"ngram\": \"Justin\", \"from\": 2384, \"to\": 2390}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Justin said 19 young farmers put their hands up to be involved in the trip, eight were pre-selected for an interview by the panel and then the final five were chosen.\", \"from\": 2398, \"to\": 2564, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Justin\", \"from\": 2398, \"to\": 2404}, {\"ngram\": \"19 young farmers\", \"from\": 2410, \"to\": 2426}, {\"ng